# Create Nothing Without Being Told

- **Create and post nothing** unless the user explicitly tells you to create or post it.
- **I create nothing on my own** — the user does not want the assistant to add, suggest, or ship features, copy, or UI without an explicit instruction.
- Do not add new sections, boxes, links, or content "to be helpful." Only change or create when the user says to do it.
